<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to CapitalHub</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      color: #333;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h2 {
      color: #333;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #666;
    }
    .cta-button {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .features {
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    .features li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <img src="https://thecapitalhub.in/static/media/logo-white.c4e4dacf1f6283c93e11.png" alt="CapitalHub Logo" style="max-width: 400px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <h2>Welcome to CapitalHub, <%= firstName %>!</h2>
    
    <p>We're thrilled to have you join our community of entrepreneurs, investors, and innovators.</p>
    
    <p>With CapitalHub, you can:</p>
    <ul class="features">
      <li>Connect with potential investors and partners</li>
      <li>Share your startup journey and milestones</li>
      <li>Access valuable resources and insights</li>
      <li>Engage with a community of like-minded professionals</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Get started by completing your profile and sharing your first update:</p>
    
    <a href="https://thecapitalhub.in/profile" class="cta-button">Complete Your Profile</a>
    
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our team is here to help!</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>The CapitalHub Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 